SENATE BILL DRS15092-MW-64
Short Title: Permanent Plates for Water & Sewer Authority. (Public)
Sponsors: Senator Sawrey (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE PERMANENT PLATES FOR WATER AND SEWER
3 AUTHORITY.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. G.S. 20-84(b) reads as rewritten:
6 "(b) Permanent Registration Plates. – The Division may issue permanent plates for the
7 following motor vehicles:
8 …
9 (21) A motor vehicle that is owned and operated by a water and sewer authority
10 created under Article 1 of Chapter 162A of the General Statutes."
11 SECTION 2. This act is effective when it becomes law.
